columns.name: api_endpoint
columns.description: The URI of the API, of the form {api-id}.execute-api.{region}.amazonaws.com

columns.name: api_key_selection_expression
columns.description: An API key selection expression. Supported only for WebSocket APIs

columns.name: disable_execute_api_endpoint
columns.description: Specifies whether clients can invoke your API by using the default execute-api endpoint.

columns.name: route_selection_expression
columns.description: The route selection expression for the API. For HTTP APIs, the routeSelectionExpression must be ${request.method} ${request.path}. If not provided, this will be the default for HTTP APIs

columns.name: created_date
columns.description: The timestamp when the API was created
